1. create app ✅
2. install nodemailer ✅
3. create homepage ✅
4. make /send-mail route (post) ✅
5. go and read the documentation of nodemailer and copy relevant code for your app (nodemailer in node js -> w3school) ✅
6. replace 'youremail@gmail.com' to your email address ✅
7. generate app password ✅
8. replace 'yourpassword' to your app password ✅